{"tid":1360561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Rockstar好game龍虎榜] 有冇巴絲玩過Manhunt/俠盜獵魔？","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:34:10.000Z","uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb8c6e136ba7b6e59b24707fea707dd751b1404","tid":1360561,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:18:34.000Z","msg":"遊戲簡介:<br />\n<br />\n他們才剛殺了凱斯（Cash）。現在，他們想要再殺他一次。<br />\n<br />\n美國到處都是荒廢、破舊的工業城鎮，那兒乏人問津、杳無人煙。在堪塞市，一切都無關緊要，剩下的只是三流恐怖片中的場景。在這裡最令人興奮的活動，就是以賦予和奪走生命為樂，而詹姆士．厄爾．凱斯（James Earl Cash），你就是這次取樂的對象。他們讓你重獲新生。現在，獵殺你的時刻到了。<br />\n<br />\n你在驚慌的喘息中驚醒。接下來必須逃跑、躲藏並且戰鬥才能求生。要是活得夠久，就有機會揪出幕後主使人。<br />\n<br />\n這是一場殘酷又血腥的消遣活動。<br />\n<br />\n第一集封面及gameplay<br />\n<img src=\"https://proxy.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20110908155348%2Frockstargamescompany%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fe8%2FManhunt.png&amp;f=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fproxy.duckduckgo.com%2Fiu%2F%3Fu%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fimg2.wikia.nocookie.net%252F__cb20110908155348%252Frockstargamescompany%252Fimages%252Fe%252Fe8%252FManhunt.png%26f%3D1&h=76c0e7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6ACO58cFUtA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6ACO58cFUtA&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9Wo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=68fda02e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6ACO58cFUtA</a><br />\n<br />\n第二集封面及gameplay<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/07/Manhunt_2_Wii_Box_Art_FINAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F0%2F07%2FManhunt_2_Wii_Box_Art_FINAL.jpg&h=b6375112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cLpnTY_Crs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_cLpnTY_Crs&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9Wo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=a4abacb4\" target=